Aniekeme Alphonsus (amụrụ na Disemba 25, 1999) bụ onye Naijirịa na-eme egwuregwu nke na-asọ mpi na sprint na ọsọ ọsọ dị n'etiti
O meriri nrite ọla edo na ọlaọcha na 4 x 100 mita relay na 100m race, na 2015 African Junior Athletics Championships.
O sonyere na ọsọ 100m na 200m na 2014 Nigerian Youth Championships (U18) nke emere na Ijebu Ode (Naijirịa)

O kwuru na nrite ọla edo mgbe ọ bịarutere na 1st, na Favor Ekezie na Abolaji Omotayo Oluwaseun na-ejedebe na ọlaọcha na ọla nchara.
Aniekeme sonyere na 2015 African Junior Athletics Championships
Na ọsọ 100m, ọ bịara na nke abụọ mgbe Tamzin Thomas gasịrị na oge nke 11.83s wee merie ọlaọcha
Naijirịa mechiri na ndekọ oge nke 44.83, ndekọ ọhụrụ nke mmeri ma merie nrite ọla edo.
Na 2015 African Youth Athletics Championships, o sonyere na Medley relay na ndị otu Naijirịa meriri nrite ọla edo na ndekọ arụmọrụ nke 2:08.71
O sonyekwara na ihe omume Long jump

O kwuru na ọ bụ ihe nrite ọlaọcha na nsonaazụ arụmọrụ nke 5.50m.
Aniekeme sonyere na 2015 Commonwealth Youth Games 100m, 200m, 4×100 mita relay, 4×200 mita relay na 4×400 mita relay
Ọ batara na 11.64 na-enweta onwe ya ihe nrite ọlaọcha na 100m ọsọ
Site na ndekọ nke 23.63 na 200m, ọ bịara na nke atọ wee merie ọla nchara
Ndị otu Naijirịa dekọrọ oge nke 45.86 wee bịa n'ọnọdụ mbụ na-enweta ihe nrite ọla edo na 4x100 mita relay
Ndị otu Naijirịa nwetakwara ihe nrite ọla edo na 4x200m na 4x400m relay.
Na 2016 IAAF World U20 Championships - Women's 200 metres na 100m, Aniekeme sonyere mana ọ rughị ọkara ikpeazụ
Ndị otu ahụ pụtara na 4x100m na 2017 World Championships mana ha agafeghị na ngwụcha.
Na All-Nigeria Track and Field Championships nke emere na Abuja, ọ na-azọrọ 1st Senior 100m National title na ndekọ oge nke 11.52s.
